header: 1. Component-Based Architecture
----
body: One of React's defining features is its component-based architecture. React applications are built by composing small, reusable components. This approach promotes code reusability, maintainability, and a clear separation of concerns. Components can be easily combined to create complex user interfaces, making development more efficient.
----
