header: 4. Large Ecosystem and Community Support
----
body: React has a vast ecosystem of libraries, tools, and extensions that enhance its capabilities. Developers can leverage popular state management solutions like Redux and MobX, routing libraries like React Router, and various UI component libraries. Additionally, React has a large and active community, providing a wealth of resources, tutorials, and support.
----
